  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ah, it’s you. Thank you again for collecting the fragments of my precious map last time. But what should I do now... I’m having such a hard time trying to piece the map back together. Is there no good way to fix this...?"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh! Now that I think about it, the petals of young #r#o55#s#k that dwell east of the village could serve as an excellent adhesive. They lure prey with their flowers, then trap them with the sticky substance coating their petals."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I think someone as strong as you could easily defeat them. Would you be willing to help me once more?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thank you! #r#o55#s#k are often seen to the east of the village. Look for the ones whose red flowers have not fully bloomed—they should be easy to spot. Please defeat them and bring me #b25 #t4000052#s#k."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "I see... I suppose you have your own reasons as well."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "You’re back already, and with the #t4000052#s I asked for!"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Thank you! Now I can finally restore my precious map."
      },
